About
Discover Our Land of Wonders
Enchanted Lakes located in the city of Malabar, is a carefully designed, bustling 55+ MHRV community with lush grounds, pool, lake, and generous space throughout the property. Our fenced community and 24-hour grounds maintenance continuously assures your comfort and privacy.
The city of Malabar is an easygoing metropolitan area with a small-town appeal. It is famous for its many outdoor activities and white sandy beaches. The city is located approximately 71 miles southeast of Orlando, 178 miles southeast of Jacksonville and 182 miles north of Miami. Major highways serving the city include Interstate 95, U.S. Routes 1 and 192 and State Routes 507 and 518.

Space Coast Living – One of CNN Travel’s Top Spots 2019
The property is directly next door to Palm Bay hospital which makes retirement living here a plus. The Orlando-Melbourne International Airport located in the center of the city is just 20 minutes from Enchanted Lakes. Malabar’s proximity to Orlando’s mega attractions like Walt Disney World and Kennedy Space Center makes Enchanted Lakes an ideal base to experience the magic that Florida’s beautiful Space Coast has to offer.
In 2019, Space Coast made it on CNN Travel’s top spots to visit, impressively judged from a pool of tourism sites not just nationwide, but worldwide! Only four U.S. destinations made the final cut – Space Coast, New York City, Grand Canyon, and Hawaii Island.
